@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@contentType = application/json
@adminToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.data.token}}
@userToken = {{loginUser.response.body.data.token}}

### Prerequisites: Run auth.rest first to get tokens

### 1. Create a Review (Positive Case - Admin)
# @name createReview
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="review.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./review.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Capture created review ID
@reviewId = {{createReview.response.body.data._id}}

### 2. Get All Reviews (Positive Case - Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews

### 3. Create Review (Negative Case - Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image": "image-data"
}

### 4. Create Review (Negative Case - Forbidden - Normal User)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image": "image-data"
}

### 5. Create Review without Image (Negative Case - 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

No image
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 6. Delete Review (Positive Case - Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reviews/{{reviewId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. Delete Review (Negative Case - Not Found - 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reviews/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
